Class OACommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.html.OAHtmlComponent
      • com.viaoa.html.OALink

          • com.viaoa.html.OACommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAToggleButton

    public class OACommand
extends OAImage
    Includes built in commands and the option to create a passthru command to a url (.jsp). If a passthru command, then OAForm setLastCommand() will be set to value of command and setLastObject() will be set (if needed). 
        [Java Code]
    OACommand cmd = new OACommand(hub,OACommand.SAVE);
    cmd.setInvisibleImageName("invisible.gif");
    cmd.setDisabledImageName("saveOff.gif");
    form.add("cmdTest", cmd);
    ....
    [HTML Code]
    <input type="image" <%=form.getCommand("cmdTest").getTags()%>">
    output =>
    <input type="image" name="oacommand_7_cmdTest" SRC="save.gif" src="test.gif">

    
    -or-
    <INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT" <%=form.getCommand("cmdTest").getTags()%>" VALUE="OK">
    output =>
    <input type="SUBMIT" name="oacommand_7_cmdTest" VALUE="OK" >
    See Also:
    OATable.addCommand(java.lang.String, com.viaoa.html.OACommand), Serialized Form
